Name: Conor O'Shea
Bio: Conor just wants Gen Z to vote. Before founding Up to Us, he spent 4 years at Tesla, helped lead Growth at Citizen, and interned for Senator Elizabeth Warren.

Name: Ava Donaldson
Role: Board of Directors, Head of Talent
Bio: Ava is the US Influencer Lead for Google Hardware. She's passionate about the intersection of culture and politics — previously running content strategy for her mother, Susan Bysiewicz's successful campaign for Lieutenant Governor of Connecticut.

Name: Sam Sheffer
Bio: Sam Sheffer is a technologist that resides in New York City. He spent his 20s working in tech media; at Engadget, The Verge, and Mashable. He now makes YouTube in his TriBeCa studio and enjoys playing video games, riding his electric longboards, and only the finest Japanese whiskey.

Name: Emily DaSilva
Bio: Emily is the COO of Outvote, where she helps hundreds of campaigns, nonprofits, unions, and national advocacy organizations mobilize supporters for sweeping change in 2020. She runs on tea and musical theatre.

Name: Brian Wright
Bio: Brian is the Head of Marketing at Six Degrees Creative, an Atlanta-based creative house that puts their outside-the-box stamp on global brand campaigns. See if you can find him in one of the 27 music videos he’s appeared in.

Name: Alex Register
Role: Head of Partnerships and Business Development
Bio: Alex is head of Marketing + Partnerships for Daisie, former VICE + Tesla

Name: Hanna Romley
Bio: Hanna works on Up to Us' content creation and brand strategy. Always manages to include a car or two.

Name: Shreya Sudarshana
Bio: Shreya is on the product management team at Disney+, working on consumer engagement and content discovery.

Name: Alex Rieflin
Bio: Alex is an independent designer building visual identity for Up to Us. He is registered to vote.

Name: Josh Svoboda
Bio: Josh is a graphic designer at WHOOP by day, and brand designer at Up to Us by night. He helps create and curate the visual identity to ensure everything looks its best.

Name: Lindsey Kennedy
Bio: Lindsey is a fiction author and editorial director based in LA. She helped develop some of the branding for up to us.

Name: Rosendo Ayala
Bio: Rosendo is a photographer and creative director living in Los Angeles.

Name: Shianne Bagget
Bio: Shianne works in sports media account management at Optimum Sports working with Gatorade, McDonalds, BioFreeeze, & Intel. She dreams of owning a D&I Sports & Entertainment media consulting firm.

Name: Angelo Saraceno
Bio: Angelo is a product manager during the day. His main goal in life is to build great civic and product experiences. It is said that he has a distinct laugh.

Name: Aaron Son
Bio: Aaron is an engineer building software to transform subscription e-commerce at Scoutside.

Name: Nik Huebecker
Bio: Nikolas is an entreprenuer and engineer currently working on a stealth startup.

Name: Anisha Sunkerneni
Bio: Anisha is a web developer and ex-medical student. She's passionate about design, medicine, technology and developing products that bring people together. Anisha enjoys asking questions that make people think.

Name: Eshita Nandini
Bio: Eshita is a Data Analyst at Shareworks by Morgan Stanley. She helps build Up to Us' website and bring creators onboard to create content.

Name: Ali Finkelstein
Bio: Ali is a "jack-of-all-trades" that graduated from MIT with a Master’s of Engineering and Bachelor’s of Science in Computer Science and Electrical Engineering. Ali is driven by innovation, with knowledge in security, databases, and systems fields.

Name: Katie Lin
Bio: Katie leads product and business strategy at Couplet Coffee and studies Information Systems at Carnegie Mellon.

Name: Long Tran
Bio: Long Tran is a software engineer currently studying Computer Science at University of California San Diego

Name: Jimmy Hsu
Bio:
Jimmy Hsu is a multidisciplinary software engineer and serial entrepreneur. Previously, he was a Fellow at On Deck, Senior Lead Software Engineer 
at WeWork & Pandora Music, and Founder at Recharge. He currently is Co-Founder of Astro Financial. He insists that 1 Doge will always be 1 Doge.

Name: Benjamin Allan-Rahill
Bio: Ben sometimes goes by his initials BJAR. He enjoys going up and down mountains and is a trained ballet dancer. Ben's currently taking the semester off from Middlebury College.
